    "description": "<strong>主要想法</strong><br><br>“Strange Town” 是一款以本地多人/多人生存为主题的角色扮演游戏。游戏的主要目标是找出并惩罚叛徒，前往这个神奇世界的“出口点”离开它，因为世界正在慢慢恶化，有毒气云开始覆盖地图。同时，一到两个玩家将成为狼人，给无辜玩家带来另一个挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/3eb79a8bef6c0216ac38c1de591b3c07.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/3eb79a8bef6c0216ac38c1de591b3c07.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/3eb79a8bef6c0216ac38c1de591b3c07.mp4?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>▶▶ <strong>特点:</strong><br><br>▶ <strong>狼人</strong>: 狼人的主要目標是破壞無辜玩家離開地圖的計劃，或者在吃了足夠的肉後變成狼人並屠殺所有無辜玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/4f5d275124b8e1432529df884cccc5cd.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/4f5d275124b8e1432529df884cccc5cd.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/4f5d275124b8e1432529df884cccc5cd.mp4?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>▶ <strong>胸部</strong>: 在地图上随机出现的箱子中打开并收集特殊道具以增强自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/2eb7c195abf3e4dcdf81bb21c9afae97.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/2eb7c195abf3e4dcdf81bb21c9afae97.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/2eb7c195abf3e4dcdf81bb21c9afae97.mp4?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>▶ <strong>肉</strong>: 某些区域出现的一些肉只能被叛徒吃掉。记住！如果一个叛徒吃了足够的肉，他们可以变成狼人。保持警惕，如果你看到有人在吃肉，立即告诉其他人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/a3a26518f9bee6ea7f52ae5787327770.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/a3a26518f9bee6ea7f52ae5787327770.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/a3a26518f9bee6ea7f52ae5787327770.mp4?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>▶ <strong>世界任务</strong>: 地图上有几个骷髅营地分布在不同的地方。如果你成功击败了所有的骷髅，这些营地会提供你任务物品或高质量的强化物品。<br><br>▶ <strong>地图</strong> : 玩家们开始在地图的第一阶段，需要在骷髅营地杀死骷髅并收集钥匙碎片。只有收集了这些钥匙碎片，玩家才能进入第二阶段，那里有出口点，让无辜的玩家结束游戏。<br><br><br><strong>STRANGE TOWN</strong> 是一个和朋友一起玩非常棒的游戏。 <strong>将其加入您的愿望清单并告诉您的朋友！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
